text: Londiani is a Kenyan town in the Kericho County. As of 2009, it had a total population of 44,953.1999 census == Transport == Londiani is located in the Kipkelion East Constituency between Nakuru and Kericho, off total-kericho highway off Nakuru-Eldoret highway about one hour drive from Nakuru town. == Statistics == * Elevation = 2325m == References == Category:Kericho County
title: Londiani
